    <div class="body">
      I for one appreciate the exercise. I know very little about what goes into actually mining, trading, using bitcoins. I've read a ton of articles on the topic but have always been hesitant to give it a try. This provides a safe way to participate and the best way to learn is by doing. So I think this is a great idea!
      
